overrideValues.value:
Sorting is applied to tables headers with the arrow always pointing to the largest value. 
It’s helpful to include an information icon with a tooltip that explains the sorting function on sortable rows

Ascending:
•  A to Z
•  0 to 9
•  January to December
•  12:00AM to 11:59PM

Descending:
•  Z to A
•  9 to 0
•  December to January
•  11:59PM to 12:00AM
